 • Anorexia is a condition where one has a constant fear of gaining weight
 • It's a mental disorder

Symptoms to look for:

• Extremely slim and unhealthy appearance
• Minimal food intake
• Excessive exercising 
• Forcible removal of food by induced vomiting 

